document_data.name: Symbaern
document_data.symbol: White [[Espruar]] s-rune on a green field
document_data.mainbody: House '''Symbaern''' was a [[sun elf]] house on [[Evermeet]] that survived the fall of [[Myth Drannor]].
document_data.Leadership: As of [[1368 DR]] it was led by [[Yalathanil Symbaern]], a reclusive wizard of more than a thousand years.
document_data.Activities: Warriors of House Symbaern were regarded as some of the finest in Evermeet's army.
document_data.Base: The house estate was located in [[Leuthilspar]]. It consisted a domed silvery structure and numerous towers and villas.
document_data.Symbol: The house symbol is a white [[Espruar]] s-rune on a green field.
document_data.Members: * '''[[Yalathanil Symbaern]]''', patriarch of the house in [[1368 DR]].
